text:
Far Rockaway Boulevard, at Mott Avenue (vantage point). The views are northeastward along the Long Island Railroad tracks and show the Far Rockaway station and the John Winkler storage plant at 1118 Foam Place.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
View 1: 1923
View 2: 1925
title: Queens: Far Rockaway Bouleva - Mott Avenue
